beer.beer_description: It’s the perfect winter ‘immune-brewster’. A strong garnet ale co-fermented with cranberry juice and with late additions of goji berries, acai berries and spirulina. Expect a refreshing tartness melding with a boozy blend of toffee and fruity malt characters. Brewed for #GABS2018.
